  {
    "id": "69340ef44bd94ffe",
    "type": "comment",
    "z": "47a279345d2c43f7",
    "name": "⚡ GAS SCHEDULER — Node-RED is the Single Control Plane",
    "info": "This tab replaces ALL GAS time-driven triggers.\n\nHOW IT WORKS:\n  1. Cron inject fires at the scheduled time\n  2. Function node preps the GAS action payload\n  3. HTTP request calls GAS web app\n  4. Result handler checks success/failure\n  5. On failure → alerts Slack #alerts\n\nTO DISABLE: Click the inject node → set to disabled\nTO RE-SCHEDULE: Click inject → change cron expression",
    "x": 360,
    "y": 40,
    "wires": []
  },
