    "type": "comment",
    "z": "47df6624715c4999",
    "name": "🔄 END-TO-END INTAKE PIPELINE",
    "info": "Webhook → Validate → Slack Alert → Create SignNow Packet → Send Signing Link → Confirm.\nFully automated — no manual steps needed.",
    "x": 340,
