    "name": "🔭 THE SCOUT — GEOGRAPHIC EXPANSION",
    "info": "Daily 5 AM scan of expansion county jails.\nTargets: Sarasota, Manatee, Glades, DeSoto, Highlands.\nHigh-value arrests get routed to Bounty Hunter.",
